title: 【Dark Mode Texture Pack】深色模式材质包【1.13/1.14/1.15/1.16】【16x】
author: 爱心魔王FHC
txt_content:
本帖最后由 爱心魔王FHC 于 2021-1-22 13:40 编辑 

深色模式材质包Dark Mode is a resource pack that adds a new dark appearance to the vanilla user interface!
Support for Bedrock Edition
Support for Java Edition *NEW!*
Designed to work in conjunction with vanilla textures
You can share this resource pack, but please refer others to my website or MCPEDL only.深色模式可以改变你的原版MC的GUI界面
支持基岩版（也支持java版，可以去原帖下载），可以与原版材质搭配使用作者: Offroaders123图片展示












材质分辨率16x支持的版本1.13/1.14/1.15/1.16下载链接: https://pan.baidu.com/s/1BiOI_zZw6UTq8Idl9Gvg-g
提取码: Dark
